label: Average price
comment: Average price at Country, Regional, County/Unitary/District Authority and London Borough level, for the given reference period.  For further information see: http://www.ons.gov.uk/economy/inflationandpriceindices/methodologies/developmentofasingleofficialhousepriceindex
